OL,4,G0540FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,6,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,7,     Gfor one last time to confront
OL,8,     Gtheir rivals. Tensions run high
OL,9,     Gas the payments are revealed and
OL,10,     Gthe winner is announced.
OL,11,G0915FFrasier
OL,12,G0945FFrasier
OL,13,G1015FThe Simpsons
OL,14,G1045FThe Simpsons
OL,15,G1115FThe Simpsons
OL,16,G1145FFour in a Bed
OL,17,     GOne pair in Portsmouth are wowed
OL,18,     Gby their room; another find the
OL,19,     Gdesign delightful. But a duvet
OL,20,     Gdisaster could spell the host's
OL,21,     Gdoom, while the parking is
OL,22,     Gutterly frightful. _WorldPoetryDay
