OL,4,G1215FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe breakfast in Bournemouth is
OL,6,     Gbrimming with quality. But sod
OL,7,     Gthe high calibre; the guests just
OL,8,     Gwant quantity. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,9,G1250FFour in a Bed
OL,10,     GPaul and Tracey host in Dorset
OL,11,     Gand aim to impress, with their
OL,12,     Gfashionable hospitality. But
OL,13,     Gsubstandard sleep leaves one
OL,14,     Gguest depressed, and feedback
OL,15,     Gpresents abnormalities.
OL,16,     G_WorldPoetryDay
