OL,4,G1320FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GAt a scenic glampsite in
OL,6,     GCornwall, there are beautiful
OL,7,     Gvistas for all. But dusty
OL,8,     Gdiscoveries, leave some guests
OL,9,     Gall snuffly - could this be the
OL,10,     Ghosts' big downfall?
OL,11,     G_WorldPoetryDay
OL,12,G1350FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GFinger-pointing, rows and
OL,14,     Gvenomous jibes; no this isn't
OL,15,     GPrime Minister's Questions. It's
OL,16,     Gpayment day on Four in a Bed -
OL,17,     Gand there's plenty of feedback
OL,18,     Gfor digestion. _WorldPoetryDay
