OL,4,G1420FKirstie and Phil's Love It or
OL,5,     FList It
OL,6,     GThere once was a fellow called
OL,7,     GPhil. He and Kirstie were rather
OL,8,     Gbrill. At loving or listing.
OL,9,     GUsing methods consisting. Of know-
OL,10,     Ghow and bargaining skill.
OL,11,     G_WorldPoetryDay
OL,12,G1525FLocation, Location, Location
OL,13,     GThe search starts with a million-
OL,14,     Gpound budget. Finding the right
OL,15,     Gplace; can Kirstie nudge it? And
OL,16,     Gcompromise is put to the test,
OL,17,     Gwhen Rebecca and Sohail's kids
OL,18,     Gfly the nest. _WorldPoetryDay
