OL,4,G1625FSleepless in Seattle
OL,5,     GClassic romcom; love in the Big
OL,6,     GApple. Long distance
OL,7,     Grelationships can be such a
OL,8,     Gbattle. Annie in Baltimore,
OL,9,     Galready spoken for, and Sam is
OL,10,     Gsleepless, up in Seattle.
OL,11,     G_WorldPoetryDay
OL,12,G1830FChannel 4 News
OL,13,G1900FThe Race for Ancient Egypt in
OL,14,     FColour
OL,15,     GEgypt takes control of its
OL,16,     Gtreasures, while experts race to
OL,17,     Gfind more. Extraordinary findings
OL,18,     Gare made at Tanis. But then the
OL,19,     Gworld goes to war. _WorldPoetryDay
