OL,4,G2000FRoman Empire by Train with Alice
OL,5,     FRoberts
OL,6,     GIn Tarragona, Alice learns how
OL,7,     Gthe Romans gained control of the
OL,8,     Gentire Med. In Cartagena, she
OL,9,     Gmarvels at subterranean riches of
OL,10,     Gsilver and lead. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G2100FBill Bailey's Vietnam
OL,12,     GIn Hanoi, Bill explores Vietnam's
OL,13,     Gcomplex relationship with life,
OL,14,     Gdeath and war; a culture defined
OL,15,     Gby spirituality, femininity and a
OL,16,     Gunique tradition at its core.
